Title: A short comment on the supersymmetric structure of Chern-Simons theory

in the axial gaugeAuthors: A. Brandhuber, M. Langer, M. Schweda, O. Piguet and S.P. Sorella

Comments: 7 pages, LATEX, UGVA---DPT 1992/11--793

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B300 (1993) 92-95

The topological supersymmetry of the pure Chern-Simons model in threedimensions is established in the case where the theory is defined in the axialgauge.